# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  STRATEGY 2 — YES+NO ARBITRAGE
#  File: strategies/YES+NO_1usd/{btc,eth,sol,xrp}/bot.py
#  Run:  python strategies/YES+NO_1usd/btc/bot.py
#
#  How it works:
#    Monitors UP and DOWN prices simultaneously.
#    When a side enters PRICE_RANGE, places a single FAK buy on that side.
#    Maximum 1 buy per side per window (no DCA, no TP, no SL).
#    Goal: buy UP + DOWN combined for < $1.00 → guaranteed profit at resolution.
#    On startup asks whether to use 5-minute or 15-minute markets.
#
#  PRICE_RANGE     Trigger band "low-high" — buys when price >= low AND <= high
#                  Example: "0.40-0.45" buys when price is between 0.40 and 0.45
#  AMOUNT_TO_BUY   USDC spent per side (UP buy + DOWN buy = 2x this amount max)
#  POLL_INTERVAL   Seconds between each price check tick (shared with Strategy 1)
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

